{"tid":1012184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車主Hades Au赤口爆粗鬧清潔工洗街灰塵沾污泊街愛車","createTime":"2019-02-07T11:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T06:10:07.000Z","uid":131157,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"07eb89227a4c0eac2350adc78dd9bfc396a87483","tid":1012184,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/927820-香港-維港會%EF%BC%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F927820-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%83%25EF%25BC%259A&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2Bcrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=1c926117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F927820-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%83%25EF%25BC%259A&h=377a12ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/927820-香港-維港會%EF%BC%9A</a><br />\n車主赤口爆粗鬧清潔工+洗街灰塵沾污泊街愛車 <br />\n<br />\n今日大年初三「赤口」，傳統上容易與人口角爭執。在大角嘴有車主相當「火爆」，以粗言怪責清潔工年初三洗街揚起灰塵，令泊街邊的私家車變髒。 <br />\n<br />\nFacebook群組「我長大於大角咀」有網民上載一張清潔工清洗街頭的照片，旁邊有幾輛聲稱，「赤口X咗佢哋幾下，個個啲車新年先打完蠟洗晒車，你哋一洗地就將啲泥塵打返晒上架車！」。 <br />\n<br />\n言論引起網民激烈抨擊，指事主無事生非、無理取鬧，「泊得街就預咗」、「清潔工初三都開工呀，咁錫車唔好泊街，攬埋返屋企啦」，「洗晒車打晒蠟唔好揸出街丫嘛，搵個套笠住佢」。 <br />\n<br />\n也有人認為應該體諒清潔工過年都無法休息，清潔街道服務市民，「唔通為咗你部車乾淨唔洗條街咩」、「初三唔駛做咩警察都要抄牌啦」、「當大家跟長輩拜年相聚時，偏偏一群年老為生計的清潔工按本分工作，還要在新正頭被樓主用粗口無理辱罵，請樓主好好檢（討）一下」。 <br />\n<br />\n不過事主拒絕認錯，反駁：「你哋都幾好笑嫁喎，初三開工關咩事？我逼佢開？泊街係預咗架車會咁？就咁睇都見到佢哋並唔係唔小心，你估條街洗地你個人行過唔小心洗到你你地會唔會出聲？真係神邏輯。到時我又會叫你怕污糟唔好出街架啦」。"},{"pid":"353a74242ea718e97ab0adf3d5d039ec368fbf59","tid":1012184,"uid":34562,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"睇錯車主口爆清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9078c0f83966b5080681208ec2ea761d10cba2","tid":1012184,"uid":131157,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"條陷家產關閉左回覆功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517c13c12bb10e7869bbc4029a9e76c60cfdbf16","tid":1012184,"uid":27247,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"傻閪車主"},{"pid":"c75e0f75fd03286a4338361881b2bca145892ec8","tid":1012184,"uid":220701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"抵停車場咪冇煩惱囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbfb0cb0037b8d4c60ef4543d46056036e87835","tid":1012184,"uid":142097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:43:24.000Z","msg":"除左講恭喜都唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"b728e30eaaa98818e0667c623ec84556aef553d7","tid":1012184,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47d66bf7870d8d4a5dda6f8153b6f0c737a1b2f","tid":1012184,"uid":107405,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"香港依家越黎越多自私既傻西<br />\n成日郁d就想公審搵認同感 又唔知自己諗法自私<br />\n個個月都幾單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8488a5ad0cfe5fba401b8c78609460b82d4773ab","tid":1012184,"uid":166792,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"到時我又會叫你怕污糟唔好出街架啦<br />\n<br />\n真係wor 又 怕污糟出乜撚野街 人地初三都要開工 整到你少少就嘈嘈閉"},{"pid":"88c3b4d51b55748f2cec21db155accfd613f0a69","tid":1012184,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"個樣好似黑社會"},{"pid":"fd125656ddc62781677bec3c48434e6af62aef11","tid":1012184,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:50:01.000Z","msg":"香港一年365日都係赤口，日撚日都有人喺街嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffe2d38e76fc78d794cadedcd22084cb02a158